data.description: This home is in a quiet area in North Killeen and is just waiting for a new owner. The HVAC system was replace in February 2023. The home is four sided brick with double paned windows. The kitchen features Oak cabinets, laminate counter tops, a double stainless steel sink with a extendable/pot filler faucet, disposal, dishwasher, food pantry and an eat in dining area. There is a large living room for entertainment and family gatherings and it features a tray ceiling with ceiling fan. The master bedroom is spacious with a large walk in closet and features a tray ceiling with a ceiling fan. The front yard is nice and the back yard is large. The back yard is fenced as well but the owner said that it is actually on the other neighbors property. Take a look at this home and lets make a deal. All measurements are deemed accurate but buyers should verify for themselves.
